text: Phrynetopsis marshalli is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1935. It is known from Sierra Leone and Ghana.BioLib.cz - Phrynetopsis marshalli. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1935
